-- Thai Rice Committee Sets Purchase Price at 15,000 Baht/Ton
-- B y   S u t t i n e e   Y u v e j w a t t a n a
-- 2013-07-01T07:34:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-01/thai-rice-committee-sets-purchase-price-at-15-000-baht-ton.html
Thailand ’s rice policy committee
decided to set support price for 100 percent unmilled, white
rice at 15,000 baht a ton for the second harvest of 2012-2013,
says Worawit Jumpeerath, budget bureau’s director general.
* The committee decided to maintain a purchase limit of 500,000
baht per family, Worawit tells reporters
* NOTE: The cabinet has yet to give final approval of the
purchase price and purchase limit
* NOTE: On June 19, the cabinet had decided to cut the purchase
price of 100-percent unmilled white rice for the second harvest
of 2012-2013 to 12,000 baht from 15,000 baht a ton.
* NOTE: On June 19, the cabinet also decided to set a purchase
limit of 500,000 baht per family  To contact the reporter on this story:
